init_text: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The nations of the world were unified under China decades ago, and the entire planet lives under a single government.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: American culture, movies, and music are all illegal.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States is reduced to a third-world country.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: President Trump is sent to a prison camp in Alaska where he works on a chain gang.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He gets to play with all sorts of chemicals and poisons, and tells funny stories about how his daddy used to call him "Little Rocket Man" when

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As for the American people, they are placed in a giant theme park where they work to build more theme parks.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: On the bright side, at least the Chinese remember what a hamburger is.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It comes with a side of fries that is really just a bunch of chopped up radishes.
